INTELLECTUAL PROPERTY

The vitality functional W(t) = Q(T,wear)·D − chi(wear)·T_norm −
E_norm·ENERGY_GAIN + omega(fatigue,T)·phase·PHASE_GAIN, the
Uncertainty-Aware term U(t) = sigma_E + alpha·(1 − f_familiarity),
the thermal energy accumulator architecture, and all associated
algorithms are proprietary intellectual property of Dimitar Kretski.

Scientific reference: DOI 10.5281/zenodo.19019599

